 <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
  <br/>
  "Cut with a knife"
  <br/>
  This sign looks like you are using your right index finger to saw  your 
  left index finger off.
  <br/>
  <br/>
  <img border="0" height="213" src="/images/knife.21.gif" width="214"/>
  <img border="0" height="213" src="/images/knife.22.gif" width="214"/>
